Reference Number: 9660703NDSJob Description: This person is responsible for the Execution of Exploration program & safety of the mining and mineral processing operations on the vessel at all times.The person is responsible and has the authority for ensuring that all legislation and regulations pertaining to the mining operations are complied with onboard, and that orders issued by authorities, classification society, and concession holders in this regard, are complied with and carried out.They are responsible for the management of all activities onboard the offshore mining vessel pertaining to the mining and mineral processing operations and acts as Companies officially appointed “Mine Manager” for the vessel in terms of the South African & Namibian mining legislation. He will have all vested authority assigned to them as outlined in the respective regulations.Responsibilities: Requirements:Qualification and Skill Benefits and Contractual information: